{"tid":979762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳香港投資者購國米3成股份","createTime":"2019-01-13T03:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T04:45:28.000Z","uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"907da069cd5886d8f3063eb366a57b6f35a45bf5","tid":979762,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0H4oW%2BgquIP99nIvOe5VJTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=54c161c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】法新社引述意大利傳媒消息指，有香港投資者準備購入印度富商Erick Thohir的31%國際米蘭股份。<br />\n<br />\n中國蘇寧集團在2016年6月以2.7億歐元收購國際米蘭68.55%的股份，而國米前老闆Erick Thohir旗下ISC仍持有球會31%的股份，法新社引述天空體育報道，印度富商的股份或快將易手，因為有沒透露名字的香港投資者準備作出收購，雖然雙方仍未作出簽署，但談判已進入後期階段，可望在幾周內完成。<br />\n<br />\n至於意大利傳媒《Il Messaggero》報道，香港投資者透過一個香港基金向國米報價，而目標更是球會最大股東中國蘇寧集團，雖然蘇寧集團無意出售，但面對投資者進一步將價格提高後，令大股東對出售作重新考慮，但多方報道中都沒有透露該香港投資者的真實身份。<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24233486292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24233486292&d=0H4oW%2BgquIP99nIvOe5VJTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b02ef0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24233486292</a>"},{"pid":"4cd292fab686737976394b8464891137fde903a6","tid":979762,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"劉嗚煒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4375ae3e84370e8d9af3f21864727b2fd7c58b64","tid":979762,"uid":40668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"印尼富商變印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}